706885f-a.text: 160-184 Sterling Place, south side, west from Flatbush to Seventh Avenues, showing also at the right foreground, the N.W. corner of Flatbush Avenue and Sterling Place. In the background next to No. 160, is a new Christian Science Church. January 1, 1937. P. L. Sperr.
